The,One,Codex,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,a,genomic,search,and,data,platform,into,their,own,applications,One,Codex,is,a,platform,designed,to,help,microbiologists,rapidly,assess,their,samples,It,provides,access,to,the,world,s,largest,index,of,bacterial,viral,and,fungal,genomes,It,comes,with,rich,sample,management,which,allows,users,to,index,search,and,compare,complex,samples